@(A.5 = 5) @fsux{Barsud}.

#lg B	cagbatuku


@(B.6 = 6-11) As fine as @wDN{An}, woman with a holy (?) head, made perfect by the …… lady! @wDN{Nanaya}, properly educated by holy @wDN{Inana}, woman who is as bright as the stars, wise lady who is available for everything, righteous sympathetic woman, lady who is always available on request, counselled by holy @wDN{Inana}, beloved by the Mistress! @wDN{Nanaya}, great judge, deity who occupies the high throne of @wSN{Unug}!

#trailer rubric	cagbatuku


@(B.12 = 12) @fsux{Šagbatuku}.

#lg C	barsud


@(C.13 = 13-16) Righteous woman who knows well the verdicts of the good decisions of the Land, @wDN{Nanaya}, who is wise in directing the city and the numerous people, exalted woman adept at holy speech, lady fitted for beauty, @wDN{Nanaya}, pride of @wTN{E-ana}, well-spoken one of the Land!

#trailer rubric	barsud


@(C.17 = 17) 2nd @fsux{barsud}.

